{
  "stem": "20745.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my aunt-- my father's sister-- took-- went with her, and we never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day, the Germans came into town, they-- they-- and they start shooting around the houses, near the houses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went into a corner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I covered myself with a-- with a basin-- my face.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't see me, but I was in a corner sitting, but I still wanted to protect my head and face.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother Eliezer-- he jumped out the window, and he was shot to death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soon after they left the same day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They killed a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They buried them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We ran to look-- look for a place where to hide.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when we thought this was going on, my father had a lot of friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They all promised him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when it came to-- they-- all they were afraid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't want to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had to come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was like in outskirts of the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't in the center.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But a few houses weren't-- weren't burned, so they let us stay there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we weren't allowed to go all over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not too many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went, maybe, to different towns-- there wasn't much room there-- maybe to some Gentile people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they took some people to work, but they sent them to camps-- to concentration camps-- to working camps, maybe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next, they-- they-- we went to the-- they took us to the ghetto, to Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A-- a few hours with by horse and buggy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the-- I don't remember how.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
